```class Solution {
    public int minMovesToMakePalindrome(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int res = 0;
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        for (int i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            if (sb.length() > 0 && sb.charAt(0) != s.charAt(i)) {
                sb.insert(0, s.charAt(i));
                res++;
            } else {
                sb.insert(0, s.charAt(i));
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
